data.description: Discover the best of both worlds with this elegant 5-bedroom, 6.5-bath home in Gainesville, GA, set on a spacious 1.5-acre lot all within a vibrant swim-tennis community. Featuring a classic 4 sided brick exterior, hardwood floors, and 9-foot ceilings, and updated kitchen. This home combines stately design with modern comforts. The main floor hosts multiple living spaces with 3 masonry fireplaces, a formal dining room, separate breakfast room, and the primary bedroom with a luxurious bath and custom closet. Enjoy the sun porch, screened porch, and outdoor seating for hours of entertaining, reading, or just enjoying the beautiful surroundings. Upstairs you will discover four bedrooms and three baths (two bedrooms with en suites and walk in closets). YouCOll love the 2-car garage with immediate mud room drop zone as you enter the home. Plus a laundry room, full bath, and possible office all before you enter in to the main living space of the home. You have a short walk to community amenities like a pool, tennis courts, playground, and dog park. This beautifully updated estate home is a keeper! Come see it quickly!
